            "text": "in it without an antecedent is better expressed in English by the impersonal, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "which one shall offer, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "or by the passive, ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "ital",
            "text": "which shall be offered. ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "(See ",
            "children": []
