            "text": "Leviticus 7:20-29",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ".) Three classes of peace offerings are specified—(1) an acknowledgment of mercies received, (2) as a vow offering, (3) as a freewill offering.",
